stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_threshold: columns_obtained > 50% of all columns
    q_check_threshold --> q_delay: columns > 50%
    q_check_threshold --> [*]: columns <= 50% (wait for more)
    q_delay --> q_reconstruct: optional random delay elapsed
    q_reconstruct --> q_iter_col: full_matrix = recover_matrix(partial_matrix, blob_count)
    q_iter_col --> q_check_sub: has next reconstructed column
    q_iter_col --> q_cleanup: no more columns
    q_check_sub --> q_gossip: node subscribed to column subnet
    q_check_sub --> q_advertise: node not subscribed to column subnet
    q_gossip --> q_iter_col: send DataColumnSidecar to mesh neighbors
    q_advertise --> q_iter_col: expose DataColumnSidecar availability
    q_cleanup --> q_check_custody: for each reconstructed column
    q_check_custody --> q_keep: column in custody requirement
    q_check_custody --> q_delete: column not in custody requirement
    q_keep --> [*]: retain DataColumnSidecar
    q_delete --> [*]: may delete DataColumnSidecar
